      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span><strong>milk</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1633512513580-x200.jpg",
