            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained cannellini beans</strong> to the pan with your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> with a very generous crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, covered, stirring occasionally for 16-17 min or until the potato is tender and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>cannellini</strong> <strong>bean & tomato stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
