    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, chop your<strong> basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped basil</strong> to the stew (save the rest for garnish!) and stir to combine</p><p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and leave to rest for a min before carefully slicing</p>",
