    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cannellini bean & tomato stew</strong> and top with the<strong> sliced crispy chicken</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining chopped basil </strong>and season with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
